'''Troy Vigil''' is an artist who has worked on a number of ''Star Wars'' works including several [[Star Wars: Essential Guides|Essential Guides]], trading cards, portfolio sets, and posters.

Troy began drawing and was inspired by the [[Original trilogy|''Star Wars'' trilogy]] at the age of eight to pursue an art career.

His professional career started in print production before he became a freelance computer artist.

Troy currently lives in Venice Beach, California with his partner, Stacey. They have eight cats.{{Mediacat|imagecat=images by Troy Vigil}}

